title: Moments after Midnights-  Initial Rankings!
description:
After the Midnights listening party, the 13 crew stumbled to the studio to share their joy and initial reactions to the album.. and this was all before that chaotic announcement!
Here are our initial thoughts and rankings! And don't worry.. Now that we've had the weekend to digest this whole album, we will do another ranking episode. You can look for that tomorrow!
Enjoy, and have fun doing all that vigilante shit!
What are your initial thoughts? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
